/mobject_update_utils/#f_always\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#manim.animation.updaters.mobject_update_utils.f_always\" title=\"Link to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>More functional version of always, where instead\nof taking in args, it takes in functions which output\nthe relevant arguments.</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">Parameters<span class=\"colon\">:</span></dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\"><p><strong>method</strong> (<em>Callable</em><em>[</em><em>[</em><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject/#manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\" title=\"manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\"><em>Mobject</em></a><em>]</em><em>, </em><em>None</em><em>]</em>)</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">Return type<span class=\"colon\">:</span></dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\"><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject/#manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\" title=\"manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\"><em>Mobject</em></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"manim.animation.updaters.mobject_update_utils.turn_animation_into_updater\">\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">turn_animation_into_updater</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">animation</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">cycle</span></span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">**</span></span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">kwargs</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/manim/animation/updaters/mobject_update_utils/#turn_animation_into_updater\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#manim.animation.updaters.mobject_update_utils.turn_animation_into_updater\" title=\"Link to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Add an updater to the animation\u2019s mobject which applies\nthe interpolation and update functions of the animation</p>\n<p>If cycle is True, this repeats over and over.  Otherwise,\nthe updater will be popped upon completion</p>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">Parameters<span class=\"colon\">:</span></dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\"><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>animation</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../manim.animation.animation.Animation/#manim.animation.animation.Animation\" title=\"manim.animation.animation.Animation\"><em>Animation</em></a>)</p></li>\n<li><p><strong>cycle</strong> (<em>bool</em>)</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">Return type<span class=\"colon\">:</span></dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\"><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject/#manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\" title=\"manim.mobject.mobject.Mobject\">Mobject</a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</dd></dl>\n\n</section>\n", "metatags": "<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["py-modindex", "Python Module Index", "", "modules"], ["reference/manim.animation.updaters.update", "update", "N", "next"], ["reference/manim.animation.updaters", "updaters", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "reference/manim.animation.updaters.mobject_update_utils.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">mobject_update_utils</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#manim.animation.updaters.mobject_update_utils.always\"><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">always()</span></code></a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference inte